    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 6 4 52 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}Yukari-chan, look out![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
